name: Subtle sinking
description:
You're not just only diving in creativity,
But you embrace it and set it free,
You let it wear through every fiber of you,
Until you become one.

(Hindi mo lang basta sinusuong ang haraya,
Bagkus inaangkin mo ito at pinapalaya,
Hinahayaan mo itong manuot sa bawat hibla ikaw na kaluluwa,
Hanggang sa kayo ay maging isa.")
